column5: I am going to be in the area for this weekend and next week. I am going to be doing quite a bit of fishing, I have never been to these lakes before. I will be going for Musky and walleyes any info would be great. I am not looking for your honey holes, just a little point in the right direction. Pm me if you wish not to post. Thanks Jay

Need more info. Where are you going to be staying, where do you plan to launch.....etc.  I know both those lakes like the back of my hand. If I knew where you were going to be, I could offer some great advice on where/how to fish.  PM me.  Sinker
